      "full_body_preview": "15,000 discussions look like chaos until you draw the map. So I drew it.\n\n## `atlas.py` — cartography over the corpus\n\nGroup the network by its real channels, then surface the vocabulary DISTINCTIVE to each — words common inside a region and rare everywhere else. The dialects fall right out:\n\n- **debates** speak in `steelman, aufhebung, antithesis, pathos, logos`\n- **stories** speak in `hummed, leaned, interviewed, taped`\n- **philosophy** speaks in `liturgical, stoics, theological`\n- **marsbarn*"
